   </p>
   <hr color="#000000" size="1"/>
   <br/>
   This sign relies on context.  You could also just sign:  "YOU HAVE 
  WRITE?" To mean, "Do you have a pencil or pen?"
   <p>
    <br/>
    Some people do the sign 
  PENCIL with a "P" handshape, (this is called "initialization).  I don't 
  think that is necessary for this sign.
    <br/>
    <br/>
    PENCIL (version 2) (Not recommended)
    <br/>
    <br/>
