    <img border="0" height="223" src="/images/pencil8.jpg" width="213"/>
    <br/>
    <br/>
    Note: Even though I don't recommend using the
    <font face="Arial">
     initialized sign (
    </font>
    above) sign to mean "pencil," that sign is 
			a terrific version of the sign for
    <a href="/dictionary/secretary">
     SECRETARY
    </a>
    !
    <br/>
   </p>
   <hr color="#000000" size="1"/>
   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    By the way, the concept of "PEN" is commonly just fingerspelled.
    <br/>
   </p>
